Popular Comedian, Ayodeji Makun, also known as AY, has welcomed his second child after thirteen years. He announced this in a video shared on his Instagram page. The birth of their second child is coming thirteen years after they had their first child, Michelle. Alongside a video, AY wrote: “Our prayers in the last thirteen years has been answered. Ayomide, thank you for making Mabel and I ‘Mummy and Daddy’ again. “Thank you for making Michelle a big sister. Thanks to everyone who kept us in their prayers and never stopped feeding us with positive vibes. “Trust in the Lord with all your heart and lean not on your own understanding. In all your ways submit to him and he will make your path straight. “God’s time is the best.”